{"tid":809640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見到幾個算有文化贏國人食KFC食到不停讚, 到時鬼國平時食乜?","createTime":"2018-09-07T10:28:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T10:33:54.000Z","uid":51701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5dd528ac0b3c8405d700e2b724ccbfc31bc5f01e","tid":809640,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:28:20.000Z","msg":"幾個睇外表唔知係贏國人, 廣東話準過香港啲學生<br />\n係間中有一個用贏語先知係贏國人<br />\n<br />\n一路食一路讚個桶餐<br />\n又話雞翼作得好食<br />\n又話薯格鬆脆<br />\n又話啲雞好食過上次深圳好多, 肉又實<br />\n薯蓉又滑又有薯味<br />\n吹到香港乜都好食 ....<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搞到我放個飯鐘好似食緊龍肉咁<br />\n到時平時鬼國啲人食開乜?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔講咁多<br />\n聽日放假過關飲喜茶先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁先係大灣區高質生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n再抬幾盒牛奶同酸奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國人飲中國飲品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中國人勃起來<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7862ee9f53b5b7f4337553ff55b31701f72d97c5","tid":809640,"uid":68219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:29:07.000Z","msg":"作得好食"},{"pid":"802b042c1510f39b783adbd9c4e65bb9c5555bd7","tid":809640,"uid":41368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:31:26.000Z","msg":"望梅止渴道理"},{"pid":"d62c78092867de78b0d24d66f574c970160c12ca","tid":809640,"uid":129664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T10:33:54.000Z","msg":"鬼國既KFC食既係咪真係雞都成問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}